gate: OPEN
sprint: S05
track: A
task: A5
title: "chore(shipping): CNH-overnight pricing constants — single source of truth (#303)"
repos: [crop-parts-services, crop-front]
priority: medium
refs:
  - CROP-parts-services#303
  - CROP-front#1437 (B6 runtime parity check depends on this landing first)
