description: |
  CNH-overnight pricing constants ($25 D&H + 15% markup) exist in 3 divergent
  copies across repos. Any price update risks silent drift between FE and BE.
  Promote to a single canonical location in packages/shared-types and remove duplicates.
  B6 (runtime parity check) depends on this task.

scope:
  in:
    - Grep: find all 3 copies of CNH-overnight constants across repos
    - Promote to packages/shared-types/shipping-constants.ts
    - Remove 2 duplicate definitions; import from canonical location in both repos
  out:
    - Changing the actual pricing values (consolidation only)
    - Any FE UI changes

acceptance:
  - Exactly one definition of CNH-overnight constants in the codebase
  - Both crop-front and crop-parts-services import from the same source
  - grep for old duplicate values returns only the canonical file

dep: none
output: packages/shared-types/shipping-constants.ts + removals in both repos
